{"tid":1663222,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"Netflix 恐怖片 隔魑治療 Eli","createTime":"2019-10-19T09:30:39.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-31T15:53:28.000Z","uid":9997,"like":8,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":31,"replies":[{"pid":"b42f5f55045718a0c7372c172d5a1064002fc1b9","tid":1663222,"uid":9997,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-19T09:30:39.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/iUgooai7aLA\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FiUgooai7aLA&d=om99xhx1cOxPLv9Q%2FbR%2FoFuXAffr%2FfAYLX%2F1af%2FGhNY%3D&h=3acd8a1a\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/iUgooai7aLA</a><br />\n<br />\n喜歡看驚悚題材電影的人，今回又有新作品可以欣賞了。知名串流平台 Netflix 今回釋出全新原創驚悚電影《Eli》（台譯：《噩夢診所》、港譯：《隔魑治療》）首發預告，若自認膽子不小，可以嘗試觀看。<br />\n<br />\n《Eli 噩夢診所》由 2012 年驚悚電影《Citadel》編導 Ciar&aacute;n Foy 執導，演員包含 Kelly Reilly、Lili Taylor、Charlie Shotwell 以及於《Stranger Things》飾演的 Max 的 Sadie Sink。<br />\n<br />\n劇情講述一個米勒家庭的兒子 Eli（伊萊）因罹患不明疾病而全身虛弱，生活起居必須與外界完全隔離。他的父母窮盡一切辦法後，把最後的希望和兒子的性命交給一位醫生，讓兒子在她的淨化屋接受先進的實驗性治療。Eli 於是開始極度密集的療程，原以為他能因此復原，怎料卻不斷出現奇怪的遭遇、幻象與折磨，使他不禁懷疑有誰可以信任，以及是誰在操控這股邪惡的力量？<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.google.com.hk/amp/s/hypebeast.com/zh/2019/10/netflix-new-horror-movie-eli-first-teaser%3famp=1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.google.com.hk%2Famp%2Fs%2Fhypebeast.com%2Fzh%2F2019%2F10%2Fnetflix-new-horror-movie-eli-first-teaser%253famp%3D1&d=om99xhx1cOxPLv9Q%2FbR%2FoFuXAffr%2FfAYLX%2F1af%2FGhNY%3D&h=3cf681d2\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.google.com.hk/amp/s/hypebeast.com/zh/2019/10/netflix-new-horror-movie-eli-first-teaser%3famp=1</a>"},{"pid":"a631e0e5147858812b0443de61702749670be816","tid":1663222,"uid":47605,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-19T09:31:19.000Z","msg":"[創意抗爭] 網民尖沙咀辦「警暴展覽」稱為喚起國際關注<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/eotKoS\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/eotKoS</a><br />\n支持長搞<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />推上國際"},{"pid":"50d2e022b09a8e363ab3721fa75ee804ef0